text: "Josie" is a 1978 song by Steely Dan and is the third single from their sixth studio album Aja. It went to number 26 in the United States and number 44 on the Easy Listening chart. It has also appeared on several live and compilation albums since its release. ==References== Category:1978 songs Category:Steely Dan songs Category:R&B; songs Category:Soft rock songs
title: Josie (Steely Dan song)
